responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "948884374453DBA63BAC4FA8AB6CC209", "My studies on Sanctus suggested that the nearby pass may be the one mentioned in old Vaelune writings, and preliminary research has shown that could be true! There appear to be some carvings along the walls, buried under the detritus of the ages. I need help to clear the dust and rubble away!")
